{
  "stem": "7157.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was-- the UNRRA camps didn't care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could have been any-- any nationality.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we went to talk to, uh-- Rachel Greene was her name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a major, and she was the head of this camp, a lady from Chicago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while we were there, a sergeant comes in by name of Shamus-- Shamus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, he was-- he was at our wedding, in Pittsburgh later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, he comes in, and he hears our name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you know my best friend, best friend through high school and school, was a guy by the name of Dave Geminder.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dave 'je-mine-der.' And, sure enough, he was a son of one of my father's brothers, who came to America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, make a long story short-- shorter-- because of that connection and because we started talking, we somehow got into this camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said to my mother, you can come, but you'll have to work, take care of children, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we got into this camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, this was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is where I learned to chew gum, and I learned to-- all the-- all the four-letter words in English.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had lots of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything was just fine at this camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, this was just, you know, the-- the highlight, considering what we'd been through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we waited our turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Basically, we waited our turn to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, to answer your question, at this point, this is when there was contact made with people in the US.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
